  - lineId: SUB_CH02_BUTLER_ADDRESS_GUESTS_001
    speakerId: Butler
    speakerDisplayName: Butler
    text: Welcome friends and gentlemen, guests of the evening, Count and Countess of Chantilly—
    minDuration: 1.25
    maxDuration: 5
    requireAdvance: 0
  - lineId: SUB_CH02_BUTLER_FOUND_G01
    speakerId: Butler
    speakerDisplayName: Butler
    text: I have found you, [Guest Name]. Dinner shall be served in the Dining Room at seven o'clock precisely. Might I record your wishes for the table?
    minDuration: 1.25
    maxDuration: 5
    requireAdvance: 1
  - lineId: SUB_CH02_BUTLER_FOUND_G02
    speakerId: Butler
    speakerDisplayName: Butler
    text: I have found you, [Guest Name]. Dinner shall be served in the Dining Room at seven o'clock precisely. Might I record your wishes for the table?
    minDuration: 1.25
