    requireAdvance: 1
  - lineId: SUB_CH02_BUTLER_FOUND_G08
    speakerId: Butler
    speakerDisplayName: Butler
    text: I have found you, [Guest Name]. Dinner shall be served in the Dining Room at seven o'clock precisely. Might I record your wishes for the table?
    minDuration: 1.25
    maxDuration: 5
    requireAdvance: 1
  - lineId: SUB_CH02_BUTLER_MEAL_ASK_001
    speakerId: Butler
    speakerDisplayName: Butler
    text: For supper, shall I put you down for the fresh monte genellion de plink, or thyme with Lillums?
    minDuration: 1.25
    maxDuration: 5
    requireAdvance: 1
  - lineId: SUB_CH02_BUTLER_SMOKE_ASK_001
    speakerId: Butler
    speakerDisplayName: Butler
    text: After dinner, shall I prepare a cigar, a pipe, or no smoke at all?
    minDuration: 1.25
    maxDuration: 5
    requireAdvance: 1
  - lineId: SUB_CH02_G01_FINAL_ACK_001
    speakerId: Guest1
    speakerDisplayName: Guest
    text: Very good. I shall present myself in the Dining Room and recover what dignity remains to us.
    minDuration: 1.25
    maxDuration: 5
    requireAdvance: 1
  - lineId: SUB_CH02_G02_FINAL_ACK_001
    speakerId: Guest2
    speakerDisplayName: Guest
    text: Very good. I shall present myself in the Dining Room and recover what dignity remains to us.
